                <h1>Boost Repository Performance with Auto Packing</h1>
                <p>Auto-packing your repository in the background can enhance overall performance by optimizing disk space and improving data retrieval times. Implementing this process ensures that unused or stale data is removed efficiently, minimizing the load time for your applications. Regular background operations help maintain a streamlined experience, ultimately boosting productivity.</p>
